Fig. 96
) emarginate, convex and acute at middle. Gonocoxae (
Fig. 95
) wide, apex of each gonocoxa with seven or eight setae from apical 1 / 6 to apex; gonocoxae connected at middle, base slender. Ventrite VIII (
Fig. 98
